{
  "version": "1.1",
  "description": "Skill activation triggers customized for this project (Next.js App Router + TypeScript).",
  "skills": {
    "skill-developer": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "high",
      "description": "Meta skill for Gemini skill/hooks/rules setup and debugging.",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "skill",
          "skills",
          "스킬",
          "skill-rules.json",
          "hook",
          "hooks",
          "훅",
          "에이전트",
          "agent",
          "코덱스 설정",
          "codex settings"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(스킬|skill).*(추가|생성|수정|트리거|규칙|활성화|디버깅)",
          "(훅|hook).*(설정|수정|추가|디버깅)",
          "(create|add|modify|debug|update).*(skill|hook|skill-rules|codex settings)",
          "(how|explain).*(skill|hook|trigger|activation)"
        ]
      }
    },
    "frontend-dev-guidelines": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "high",
      "description": "Frontend patterns for this Next.js App Router + React + TypeScript project.",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "frontend",
          "프론트엔드",
          "next",
          "next.js",
          "app router",
          "react",
          "component",
          "컴포넌트",
          "ui",
          "페이지",
          "page",
          "styling",
          "스타일"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(만들|추가|수정|구현|리팩터링).*(컴포넌트|페이지|ui|프론트엔드)",
          "(create|add|build|update|edit|implement).*(component|page|ui|frontend|next)",
          "(스타일|레이아웃|디자인).*(컴포넌트|페이지|ui)",
          "(style|layout|design).*(component|page|ui)"
        ]
      },
      "fileTriggers": {
        "pathPatterns": [
          "app/**/*.ts",
          "app/**/*.tsx",
          "components/**/*.ts",
          "components/**/*.tsx",
          "lib/**/*.ts",
          "types/**/*.ts"
        ],
        "pathExclusions": [
          "**/*.test.ts",
          "**/*.test.tsx",
          "**/*.spec.ts",
          "**/*.spec.tsx",
          "**/*.d.ts"
        ],
        "contentPatterns": [
          "'use client'",
          "from 'next/",
          "from \"next/",
          "use(State|Effect|Memo|Callback|Ref)",
          "export default function"
        ]
      }
    },
    "flutter-dev-guidelines": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "high",
      "description": "Flutter + Dart development patterns for widget architecture, state management, performance, testing, and mobile release.",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "flutter",
          "플러터",
          "dart",
          "다트",
          "widget",
          "위젯",
          "riverpod",
          "bloc",
          "provider",
          "state management",
          "상태 관리",
          "상태관리",
          "ios",
          "iOS",
          "android",
          "apk",
          "ipa",
          "pubspec",
          "pub.dev",
          "materialapp",
          "MaterialApp",
          "cupertinoapp",
          "CupertinoApp",
          "mvvm",
          "clean architecture",
          "클린 아키텍처",
          "flutter favorite",
          "repository",
          "usecase",
          "use case",
          "viewmodel",
          "view model",
          "model",
          "entity",
          "dto",
          "mapper",
          "value object",
          "immutable",
          "dependency injection",
          "di",
          "get_it",
          "injectable",
          "composition root",
          "service locator"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(flutter|dart|플러터|다트).*(구현|개발|수정|리팩터링|디버깅|최적화|테스트)",
          "(widget|위젯|화면|state management|상태관리).*(추가|수정|구현|최적화)",
          "(ios|android|apk|ipa|pubspec).*(빌드|배포|설정|오류|에러)",
          "(create|add|implement|update|refactor|debug|optimize).*(flutter|dart|widget|riverpod|bloc|provider|ios|android)",
          "(mvvm|clean architecture|클린 아키텍처).*(적용|설계|구현|리팩터링)",
          "(repository|use ?case|view ?model).*(구현|분리|설계|테스트)",
          "(flutter favorite|pub\\.dev).*(패키지|의존성|선정|검토|추가)",
          "(model|entity|dto|mapper|value object|immutable).*(설계|분리|매핑|변환|직렬화|역직렬화|마이그레이션)",
          "(모델|엔티티|dto|매퍼|값 객체|불변).*(설계|분리|매핑|변환|호환성|마이그레이션)",
          "(dependency injection|\\bdi\\b|get_it|injectable|composition root|service locator).*(구성|설정|주입|바인딩|교체|테스트)",
          "(의존성 주입|컴포지션 루트|서비스 로케이터).*(구성|설정|주입|바인딩|교체|테스트)"
        ]
      },
      "fileTriggers": {
        "pathPatterns": [
          "**/*.dart",
          "lib/**/*.dart",
          "test/**/*.dart",
          "integration_test/**/*.dart",
          "android/**",
          "ios/**"
        ],
        "pathExclusions": [
          "**/*.g.dart",
          "**/*.freezed.dart"
        ],
        "contentPatterns": [
          "MaterialApp",
          "CupertinoApp",
          "Widget build\\(BuildContext",
          "StatelessWidget",
          "StatefulWidget",
          "Riverpod|Bloc|Provider",
          "pubspec.yaml",
          "fromJson\\(",
          "toJson\\(",
          "class\\s+\\w*Model",
          "class\\s+\\w*Dto",
          "class\\s+\\w*Entity",
          "class\\s+\\w*Mapper",
          "Repository",
          "UseCase",
          "GetIt",
          "@injectable",
          "serviceLocator|service_locator"
        ]
      }
    },
    "backend-dev-guidelines": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "medium",
      "description": "Backend/API patterns for route handlers, services, validation, and data access.",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "backend",
          "백엔드",
          "api",
          "endpoint",
          "엔드포인트",
          "route",
          "라우트",
          "controller",
          "service",
          "middleware",
          "validation",
          "prisma",
          "zod"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(백엔드|api|엔드포인트|라우트).*(추가|수정|구현|테스트|리팩터링)",
          "(create|add|implement|build|fix).*(route|endpoint|api|controller|service|middleware)",
          "(error|예외|에러).*(처리|핸들링|모니터링|sentry)"
        ]
      },
      "fileTriggers": {
        "pathPatterns": [
          "app/api/**/*.ts",
          "app/api/**/route.ts",
          "backend/**/*.ts",
          "server/**/*.ts",
          "api/**/*.ts"
        ],
        "pathExclusions": [
          "**/*.test.ts",
          "**/*.spec.ts"
        ],
        "contentPatterns": [
          "Next(Request|Response)",
          "router\\.",
          "app\\.(get|post|put|delete|patch)",
          "export\\s+class\\s+.*(Controller|Service)",
          "prisma\\.",
          "zod"
        ]
      }
    },
    "route-tester": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "medium",
      "description": "Guidelines for testing authenticated routes (JWT/cookie style auth).",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "route test",
          "test route",
          "endpoint test",
          "api test",
          "라우트 테스트",
          "엔드포인트 테스트",
          "api 테스트",
          "인증 테스트",
          "jwt",
          "cookie auth"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(라우트|엔드포인트|api).*(테스트|검증|디버깅)",
          "(test|verify|debug).*(route|endpoint|api|auth|jwt|cookie)"
        ]
      },
      "fileTriggers": {
        "pathPatterns": [
          "app/api/**/route.ts",
          "**/routes/**/*.ts",
          "scripts/test-*.js",
          "scripts/test-*.ts"
        ],
        "contentPatterns": [
          "router\\.(get|post|put|delete|patch)",
          "app\\.(get|post|put|delete|patch)",
          "cookies?\\(",
          "authorization"
        ]
      }
    },
    "error-tracking": {
      "type": "domain",
      "enforcement": "suggest",
      "priority": "high",
      "description": "Error handling and monitoring patterns, including Sentry integration.",
      "promptTriggers": {
        "keywords": [
          "error handling",
          "에러 처리",
          "예외 처리",
          "exception",
          "monitoring",
          "모니터링",
          "sentry",
          "captureexception",
          "error tracking"
        ],
        "intentPatterns": [
          "(에러|예외).*(추적|모니터링|sentry|핸들링)",
          "(add|setup|implement|fix).*(sentry|error handling|monitoring|exception)"
        ]
      },
      "fileTriggers": {
        "pathPatterns": [
          "app/api/**/*.ts",
          "app/**/instrument.ts",
          "lib/**/*.ts",
          "server/**/*.ts",
          "backend/**/*.ts"
        ],
        "contentPatterns": [
          "@sentry",
          "Sentry\\.",
          "captureException",
          "captureMessage",
          "try\\s*\\{",
          "throw\\s+new\\s+Error"
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "notes": {
    "enforcement_types": {
      "suggest": "Suggests a relevant skill without blocking execution.",
      "block": "Blocks action until the required skill is used.",
      "warn": "Shows a low-priority warning only."
    },
    "priority_levels": {
      "critical": "Always show when matched.",
      "high": "Show for strong matches.",
      "medium": "Show for clear but less urgent matches.",
      "low": "Show for optional context."
    },
    "customization": {
      "pathPatterns": "Keep these aligned with actual project folders.",
      "keywords": "Include both Korean and English user prompt styles.",
      "intentPatterns": "Use broad regex first, then tighten if false positives appear."
    }
  }
}
